    <li>subject_story->spent a summer recovering from being slashed by an escaped slave's hand talon</li>
    <li>subject_story->was working in security, scanning visitors to the hall, when the cyborg attempted to enter</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->crafting compact bionic weapons</li>
  -->
  <CompactWeaponry.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->小型武器</li>
    <li>subject_story->被聘為偵探，過程中膝釘不止一次救了他的命</li>
    <li>subject_story->花了一個夏天從逃跑奴隸的手爪抓傷中康復</li>
    <li>subject_story->正在安全部門工作，掃描大廳的訪客，而此時機器人正嘗試進入</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->製作小型仿生武器</li>
  </CompactWeaponry.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: flesh shaping -->
  <FleshShaping.label>軀體整形</FleshShaping.label>
  <!-- EN: Craft bionics which induce the reshaping of natural flesh, usually for the purposes of aesthetic enhancement or personal pleasure. -->
  <FleshShaping.description>製作仿造自然軀體的仿生產品。通常用於提升美感或個人樂趣。</FleshShaping.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->aesthetic surgery</li>
    <li>subject_story->halted the population decline on the urbworld, by distributing free love enhancers and lavish drugs</li>
    <li>subject_story->was hired as chief flesh-shaper for an aesthetics clinic, spending their days making shapely limbs</li>
    <li>subject_story->gathered the glitterworld children around the campfire and told horror stories about getting their non-aesthetic noses back</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->crafting aesthetic bionics</li>
  -->
  <FleshShaping.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->美學手術</li>
    <li>subject_story->藉由分發免費的情愛增強裝置和藥物，阻止了城市世界人口的下降</li>
    <li>subject_story->被聘為美容診所的首席塑形師，整日製作美觀的肢體</li>
    <li>subject_story->將閃耀世界的孩子們聚集在營火邊，講述把他們的美型鼻拿下來的恐怖故事</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->製作美容相關的仿生物</li>
  </FleshShaping.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
